HEADWORD: Justice
<hw>Jus"tice</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To administer
justice to.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Justiceable</ent>⟦br⟧
